</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-02-02-0152-fn-0001-ptr" id="GEWN-03-02-02-0152-fn-0001">1</a>

   <p>Letter not found.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-02-02-0152-fn-0002-ptr" id="GEWN-03-02-02-0152-fn-0002">2</a>
	
   <p>For the Virginia conventions military preparations, see <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-01-02-0275&amp;expandNote=GEWN-03-01-02-0275-fn-0001#GEWN-03-01-02-0275-fn-0001" class="document">Burwell Bassett to GW, 30 Aug. 1775, n.1</a>, and <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-01-02-0314" class="document">Peyton Randolph to GW, 6 Sept. 1775</a>. See also <span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ William Waller Hening, ed. &lt;i&gt;The Statutes at Large; Being a Collection of All the Laws of Virginia, from the First Session of the Legislature, in the Year 1619&lt;/i&gt;. 13 vols. 181923. Reprint. Charlottesville, Va., 1969. ]">9 Hening 935, 7173</span>.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-02-02-0152-fn-0003-ptr" id="GEWN-03-02-02-0152-fn-0003">3</a>

   <p>See GW to John Augustine Washington, 10 Sept. 1775.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-02-02-0152-fn-0004-ptr" id="GEWN-03-02-02-0152-fn-0004">4</a>

   <p>See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-02-02-0236" class="document">Lund Washington to GW, 29 Oct. 1775</a>.</p>

</div>
